726819f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway,south from 78th Avenue, showing the Parkway passing under the Independent Subway bridge and the Union Turnpike bridge. This area is a point of juncture for
several of the borough's principal highways.

P. L. Sperr    View 1: February 10, 1937
View 2: April 23, 1936
